robert gordon " bob " mackie ( born march 24 , 1940 ) is an american fashion designer , best known for his dressing of entertainment icons such as joan rivers , cher , rupaul , barbara eden , bette midler , diana ross , judy garland , liza minnelli , tina turner , carol burnett and mitzi gaynor .

the emmys : bob mackie sewed up a costume design emmy for her variety special " men , movies and carol "

